## Data Files

### Included in Repo
- `full_data.csv` - Academy Awards data
- `the_oscar_award.csv` - Alternative Oscar data format
- `title.ratings.tsv.gz` - IMDb ratings file

### Download Separately
- `title.basics.tsv.gz` - Download from IMDb: https://datasets.imdbws.com/
  - Contains genre information needed for the analysis
  - Too large for GitHub
  - Place it in the project root directory after cloning
